Package gw.api.exposure

Class OwnedRelatedExposureFilterSetBase

java.lang.Object
gw.api.filters.FilterSetBase
gw.api.exposure.ExposureFilterSetBase
gw.api.exposure.OwnedRelatedExposureFilterSetBase
Direct Known Subclasses:
DesktopExposureFilterSet, TeamExposureFilterSet, VacationExposureFilterSet
public abstract class OwnedRelatedExposureFilterSetBase extends ExposureFilterSetBase
Abstract exposure filter set that adds compound filters based on owned and related exposures to the ExposureFilterSetBase. The owned and related filter sets are abstract and must be provided by subclassers.
